    "attributes": {
        "action": "Provide women with devices to alert police/local authorities of harassment/abuse",
        "additional_details": "Every woman/teenage girl should feel safe while out in public or even walking down the street alone in the dark. As a woman myself, I do not feel safe walking the streets at night and refuse to go out alone after the sun begins to set. This shouldn\u2019t be the case.",
        "background": "A simple key-ring fitted with a silent panic button that sends an alert and details of a person\u2019s location to their local authority/the police could make all the difference.",
